Package: jaspBreuschPagan
Type: Package
Title: Breusch-Pagan Test Module for JASP
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-05-21
Author: Your Name
Website: jasp-stats.org
Maintainer: Your Name <you@example.com>
Description: Performs the Breusch-Pagan test for heteroskedasticity in linear
  regression. Fits the main regression, takes the squared residuals, runs the
  auxiliary regression and reports the LM = n * R^2 statistic with its
  chi-squared p-value. Both the studentized (Koenker) and the original (1979)
  variants are available.
